task.summary: Fixed code issues found with analysis tool.
Added junit tests for ProjectConfig and ProgramConfig; Reworked some of the configuration code along the way.
Added junit tests for ProjectConfig and RuntimeConfig
Added ProjectConfigFactory functionality and associated junit tests.
Fleshed out some of the TestCase functionality.

Added more tests concentrating on test case error handling and reporting; Refined test case error handling in the process to handle all derivations of Throwable in order to "sand box" all script issues.
Added tests for RobustScript. Redefined RobustScript behavior in terms of retries.
Implemented MasterScriptFactory and added junit tests for it.
Refactored test case result files into separate package.
Fixed caching behavior of script info factor to cache per file type per project, rather than just per project.
Refactored initialization properties of the IBaseScript into one initialization function.
